rows.label: qst701710_msg0001
rows.name:
...I thought you'd be a little
shaken, but you're annoyingly calm.

rows.label: qst701710_msg0002
rows.name:
Not really. But you can
think what you like.

rows.label: qst701710_msg0003
rows.name:
I always thought this day would come.
I've long since made up my mind.

rows.label: qst701710_msg0004
rows.name:
Is it true? Did you
really... my sister...

rows.label: qst701710_msg0005
rows.name:
It's as good as if I killed her. If
I hadn't dreamt such an unfitting
dream, she wouldn't have had to die.

rows.label: qst701710_msg0006
rows.name:
Why did I even think I
wanted to live with her...

rows.label: qst701710_msg0007
rows.name:
She... often talked about having someone
she wanted to support. That she wanted
to help that person start a new life.

rows.label: qst701710_msg0008
rows.name: ...That's an old story.

rows.label: qst701710_msg0009
rows.name:
Kill me. You have the right.
I've eliminated everyone
involved. I'm the only one left.

rows.label: qst701710_msg0010
rows.name:
If you kill me, it will all be over.
Your revenge, and my atonement.

rows.label: qst701710_msg0011
rows.name: You...

rows.label: qst701710_msg0012
rows.name: ...This is bad!

rows.label: qst701710_msg0013
rows.name: Who will you side with?

rows.label: qst701710_msg0014
rows.name: Jelyco

rows.label: qst701710_msg0015
rows.name: Dio

rows.label: qst701710_msg0101
rows.name:
Jelyco-san will be fine.
Let's watch a little longer.

rows.label: qst701710_msg0102
rows.name:
Hey, you said atonement, didn't you? Is
that about the help you've been giving
people without receiving proper compensation?

rows.label: qst701710_msg0103
rows.name:
...I know it's not nearly
enough. That's why...

rows.label: qst701710_msg0104
rows.name:
Don't you dare say you'll make
up for it by dying. My sister
would be even sadder!!

rows.label: qst701710_msg0105
rows.name:
You want to die because you want to
be at ease. You just want to bask
in the feeling of having atoned!

rows.label: qst701710_msg0107
rows.name:
I don't care whether you live
or die, but I won't let you
waste my sister's feelings.

rows.label: qst701710_msg0108
rows.name:
Stop being so self-absorbed.
When you've cooled your head,
we'll have a strategy meeting.

rows.label: qst701710_msg0109
rows.name: Huh? For what?

rows.label: qst701710_msg0110
rows.name:
We're going to crush the Bloody
Lobsters! We are!! So that we can
start a new life from now on!!!

rows.label: qst701710_msg0111
rows.name:
I can't do anything about them
by myself. If you have free time,
help me and atone, you idiot.

rows.label: qst701710_msg0112
rows.name:
Haha, why does it have to be
like this... It's absurd.

rows.label: qst701710_msg0113
rows.name:
Why are you siblings, you and
your sister, so alike...

rows.label: qst701710_msg0114
rows.name: Is the brawl over, mo?

rows.label: qst701710_msg0115
rows.name:
I was worried and came to
see, mo. What happened, mo?

rows.label: qst701710_msg0116
rows.name: Um, there were various circumstances.

rows.label: qst701710_msg0117
rows.name:
I'm sorry for the disturbance.
It's all right now...

rows.label: qst701710_msg0118
rows.name:
A past you want to redo,
huh? Why are we so bound
by this thing called fate?

rows.label: qst701710_msg0119
rows.name: ...I've been curious for a while.

rows.label: qst701710_msg0120
rows.name:
Is your detached way of thinking
related to you becoming a Man-Eater?

rows.label: qst701710_msg0121
rows.name:
You're unusually sharp. Have
you taken an interest?

rows.label: qst701710_msg0122
rows.name: I was just curious as a fellow Blade.

rows.label: qst701710_msg0123
rows.name:
Don't. You'll just become
a half-wit. Like me.

rows.label: qst701710_msg0124
rows.name: ...Is that really so?

rows.label: qst701710_msg0125
rows.name:
There's no need to be so certain. At the very
least, if the person has made a choice and
decided not to regret it, that's another story.

rows.label: qst701710_msg0126
rows.name: ...Shin?

rows.label: qst701710_msg0127
rows.name:
If you think of yourself as a half-wit,
you become one. You should just think of
it as getting the best of both worlds.

rows.label: qst701710_msg0128
rows.name: Why are you so positive?

rows.label: qst701710_msg0129
rows.name:
If you want to move forward, you
have to look forward, don't you?

rows.label: qst701710_msg0130
rows.name:
Honestly... Being with you all makes
me feel like I'm losing my mind.

rows.label: qst701710_msg0201
rows.name: We have to stop Jelyco-san!

rows.label: qst701710_msg0202
rows.name: Tch... don't get in my way!
